item.title: [562/668] Project Dungeonfest/Derbyscape Client Jarring Help
item.dc:creator: @emptyone999 emptyone999
item.description:
@emptyone999 wrote:

[color=]You are not supposed to put it here but you can put in help but this time i will help[/color]

OK first get Jarmaker - www.goldenstudios.or.id/products/utilities/jarmaker/index.php
2. for output directory put desktop
3.change the *.jar to you client name or client.jar
4.for input put just the whole folder of Project Dungeonfest
5.and for class is RunClient ------------- remeber to make R, and C captial. and just put RunClient not RunClient.java/class
6.create jar and your done. if you changed something in client folder remake the jar.
